{"tid":421011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：與北韓談判是浪費時間","createTime":"2017-10-02T00:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T07:46:47.000Z","uid":20933,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"17d433c17f1d813263ab6f71b9ffb66bdaf6554f","tid":421011,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T00:56:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國總統特朗普指，與北韓領袖金正恩談判是浪費時間。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周日在社交網站帖文指，已經告知國務卿蒂勒森嘗試與「火箭人」談判根本是浪費時間，認為蒂勒森應該省回氣力。蒂勒森在周六結束訪華前，首次承認美國有兩、三條渠道可與北韓直接溝通，正嘗試了解平壤方面是否願意就放棄核武展開對話。<br />\n<br />\n另外，韓聯社引述南韓軍方消息報道，南韓正與美國協調美軍列根號航空母艦戰鬥群，在本月十五日與南韓海軍於朝鮮半島東部海域進行探測、追蹤和攔截北韓彈道導彈的高強度演習。有駐韓美軍官員指暫時未有軍演的時間，可能在本月二十日左右，視乎情況而定。"},{"pid":"574b50955fc48aa246fcc523db86fb3b58f1fb9a","tid":421011,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T00:56:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=237974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D237974&d=PiJ%2B0Jqmi8IWXWOz%2BVXe8MmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=665353bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D237974&h=dad8304b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=237974</a>"},{"pid":"b1cbc63410cc527eb81f9a5a76dd5edbfbf04c42","tid":421011,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T00:57:25.000Z","msg":"得個講字"},{"pid":"58474df384069a58c1e619c8386c3f78932b6bca","tid":421011,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T00:57:54.000Z","msg":"應該到時核平列根號<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80cf4da3ca3a81919cbf2b474048fc6174d9978","tid":421011,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:41:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 真係要打嘅話國防部㩒個制北韓就變焦土啦"},{"pid":"a4bd540a2ffde820f56230947401308f63f3ac17","tid":421011,"uid":13149,"like":1,"dislike